snippet.title: The Rip | Official Teaser | Netflix
snippet.description:

As outside forces learn about the size of the seizure, everything is called into question ‚Äî including who they can rely on. Starring Matt Damon and Ben Affleck & Directed by Joe Carnahan, The Rip is only on Netflix, January 16.

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81915745

Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with over 300 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. snippet.title: Minecraft LIVE Official Trailer ‚Äì September 2025
snippet.description:
Minecraft LIVE is the show to watch if you want to learn that latest news from the world of Minecraft. The next Minecraft LIVE will be broadcast on September 27 at 7PM CEST/10AM PDT.

We‚Äôll feature the inside scoop on unannounced game drops, insight from our developers, and more!
After the broadcast, stay tuned in for the Deep Dig After Show where our developers and guests show off the new features, often resulting in chaos. Vu Bui will return as host and attempt to keep things running smoothly. Good luck to that guy!

See you there! September 27 ! Watch it at https://www.minecraft.net, YouTube, Twitch, Instagram or TikTok.

snippet.title: The Sims 4 Adventure Awaits | Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Pre-order The Sims‚Ñ¢ 4 Adventure Awaits Expansion Pack*, available Oct 2: https://www.ea.com/games/the-sims/the-sims-4/buy/addon/the-sims-4-adventure-awaits-expansion-pack Order now through Nov 13 for the Warm & Cozy Digital Content**; the Toasty Tower Lamp, Toast-Tea Kettle, and Toasty Tootsies Socks.

Start your adventure: https://www.ea.com/games/the-sims/the-sims-4/news/adventure-awaits-expansion-pack

Want to see more Sul Sul Island? Follow The Sims social channels for more adventures!

Get ready to break free from the everyday with daring activities and Getaways. Getaways are more than vacations, they are experiences you design! Set a schedule and even add rules. Elimination Rules ‚Äì like skill or relationship gains ‚Äì will have Sims competing to outlast each other. Create a kids‚Äô camp, fitness retreat, romantic contest, or anything else you can imagine!

Also, create Custom Venues, where you can design, build and decorate, deciding what kinds of activities and roles are assigned. Share your creation to the Gallery for other Simmers to download and us for their own Getaways!

Live a more adventurous life with new skills: Entomology, Diving, Archery and Papercrafts. Make classic crafts like paper planes, catch and raise butterflies, make a splash with new diving boards, and hit the bullseye! These activities are for both kids and grown-ups, as are the Diving Board, Waterslide, and Kayak. Get out there and explore the water! Active Adult Sims will enjoy working out with Spin Bikes and Free Weights, and everyone will enjoy drinking a refreshing smoothie from the new Blender.

Childhood is an especially adventurous time. Customize Modular Playgrounds with slides and different platforms for a ton of Childhood fun. Kids can challenge each other with games like Hide and Seek or Rock, Paper, Scissors, and even have Imaginary Friends! Choose from four different Imaginary Friend dolls and four different personalities: Goofball, Competitive, Creative, and Evil.

Available October 2 at 10AM PT on EA App PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, PlayStation¬Æ4, and PlayStation¬Æ5. Pre-order now: https://www.ea.com/games/the-sims/the-sims-4/buy/addon/the-sims-4-adventure-awaits-expansion-pack

*Requires The Sims 4 & all game updates. For PC, see minimum system requirements for the pack.

**CONDITIONS AND RESTRICTIONS APPLY. https://www.ea.com/games/the-sims/the-sims-4/buy/addon/the-sims-4-adventure-awaits-expansion-pack

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It‚Äôs unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX ‚Äî interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything ‚Äî be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer ‚ÄúCapture the Flag‚Äù game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (‚ÄúRobux‚Äù). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

snippet.description:

THE NEW ALBUM:
Mammoth - The End out 10/24/25

ON TOUR:

Dec 2 ‚Äì Kansas City, MO ‚Äì Uptown Theater
Dec 3 ‚Äì Denver, CO ‚Äì Ogden Theatre
Dec 6 ‚Äì Tempe, AZ ‚Äì Marquee Theatre
Dec 7 ‚Äì Anaheim, CA - House Of Blues


GRAMMY¬Æ Award-nominated songwriter, vocalist, multi-instrumentalist, and producer Wolfgang Van Halen continues to separate Mammoth from the pack. The music stands alone on a foundation anchored by his impressive sonic proficiency (across drums, bass, keys, and guitar) and airtight arena-size hooks with unforgettable vocals. He harbors an irresistible signature sound, inventive vision, and incomparable identity vaunted by a fervent global fanbase. For as unique as the music is, his story so far proves to be just as unprecedented. This is arguably the first hard rock act to genuinely break out from ground zero in the 2020‚Äôs, generating north of 100 million streams, toppling charts, and selling out headline tours less than five years since its debut. Back in 2021, Mammoth‚Äôs first offering, Mammoth WVH, took flight, bowing at #12 on the Billboard 200 and capturing #1 on three Billboard charts‚ÄîTop Hard Rock Albums, Top Independent Albums, and Top Rock Albums. ‚ÄúDistance‚Äù soared as the first of two #1 Rock Radio Hits and earned a GRAMMY¬Æ Award nomination for ‚ÄúBest Rock Song.‚Äù Two years later, Mammoth II only saw him pick up the pace. It debuted in the Top 5 of the Billboard Top Album Sales Chart in addition to bringing him back to #1 on the Top Hard Rock Albums Chart. It incited widespread applause from Rolling Stone, Guitar World, GRAMMY.com, Classic Rock, American Songwriter, and KERRANG! The band canvased the globe with Metallica and Pantera and supported Foo Fighters in North America as well as filling houses on their own. They performed on ABC‚Äôs Jimmy Kimmel LIVE!, at MusiCares 2024 gala in honor of Jon Bon Jovi, and Wolf took the stage at the Rock and Roll Hall of Fame¬Æ Induction of Ozzy Osbourne. Now, Wolfgang pushes forward on Mammoth‚Äôs third full-length LP.

Connect with Mammoth at:
Website: www.mammoth.band
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/MammothWVH
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/mammothwvh/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/MammothWVH
YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/@Mammoth

#Mammoth #WVH #MammothWVH #wolfgangvanhalen

snippet.title: CHAINSAW MAN ‚Äì THE MOVIE: REZE ARC | Dub Trailer | Crunchyroll
snippet.description:
Everyone‚Äôs after his chainsaw heart.

For the first time, see Chainsaw Man - The Movie: Reze Arc exclusively in movie theatres October 24. Watch the trailer now. #ChainsawManMovie

For the first time, Chainsaw Man slashes his way onto the big screen in an epic, action-fueled adventure that continues the hugely popular anime series. Denji worked as a Devil Hunter for the yakuza, trying to pay off the debt he inherited from his parents, until the yakuza betrayed him and had him killed. As he was losing consciousness, Denji‚Äôs beloved chainsaw-powered devil-dog, Pochita, made a deal with Denji and saved his life. This fused the two together, creating the unstoppable Chainsaw Man. Now, in a brutal war between devils, hunters, and secret enemies, a mysterious girl named Reze has stepped into his world, and Denji faces his deadliest battle yet, fueled by love in a world where survival knows no rules.

Directed by: Tatsuya Yoshihara 
 
Based on the original work ‚ÄúChainsaw Man‚Äù by Tatsuki Fujimoto (Serialized in Shueisha‚Äôs ‚ÄúShonen Jump+‚Äù)

Mengapa Marvel me-reboot MCU, semua film Marvel dan acara TV Disney plus Marvel dengan Avengers 6 Secret Wars. Dan apa yang akan berubah dengan semua Avengers, New Iron Man, Mutan X-Men seperti Wolverine, Deadpool, Fantastic Four, Ghost Rider, Spider-Man, dan karakter Marvel lainnya yang sebelumnya tidak dapat digunakan seperti yang mereka inginkan di film-film sebelumnya.

Il nuovo teaser dei fratelli Russo per Avengers Doomsday. I Fantastici Quattro incontrano gli Avengers, analisi del trailer di Avengers Doomsday del 23¬∞ anniversario e Easter Egg. Nuovi personaggi, il piano generale del Dottor Destino, Deadpool, Spider-Man. Problemi sul set delle riprese di Avengers Doomsday. Il prossimo progetto di Ryan Reynolds su Deadpool, film sulla X-Force, Avengers Doomsday, piani per Secret Wars. Annuncio di Deadpool 4. Ryan Reynolds spiega il futuro dei film e delle serie TV di Deadpool alla Marvel. Spiegazione del piano di Avengers 6 Secret Wars per gli X-Men. Saga dei Mutanti della Fase 7 della Marvel, nuovi film sugli X-Men.

Perch√© Ryan Reynolds √® stato citato in giudizio per Deadpool e Wolverine. Battute Marvel, scene eliminate, causa tra Ryan Reynolds e Blake Lively. Cosa succeder√† di conseguenza. E perch√© Ryan Reynolds non deve preoccuparsi. E come la Marvel, Deadpool e Wolverine siano stati coinvolti nella causa.

X-23, Wolverine contro Hulk, scene eliminate di Gambit, scene eliminate di Blade, Sabretooth, Wolverine contro Sabretooth. Battute su Deadpool contro Disney, battute su Kevin Feige e la rottura della quarta parete. Battute sulla scena post-credit di Deadpool e Wolverine. Scena con Iron Man malvagio, scena con il cameo di The Punisher, scene sugli X-Men, altre varianti di Deadpool, altre varianti di Wolverine. Spiegazione dell'Adamantio. Riferimenti a Daredevil con Ben Affleck, Elektra, Perch√© Deadpool salva Wolverine, Gli X-Men, I Fantastici Quattro e Deadpool salvano l'MCU. Come Deadpool e Wolverine preparano Avengers 6 Secret Wars con Battleworld e Loki, che si conclude con Easter Egg del crossover con Dio Loki.

Perch√© la Marvel sta riavviando l'MCU, tutti i film Marvel e le serie TV Marvel di Disney+ con Avengers 6 Secret Wars. E cosa cambier√† con tutti gli Avengers, il Nuovo Iron Man, i Mutanti degli X-Men come Wolverine, Deadpool, i Fantastici Quattro, Ghost Rider, Spider-Man e altri personaggi che la Marvel non era riuscita a usare come voleva nei film precedenti.

Spiegazione dei piani di reboot dell'MCU Marvel. Cosa √® successo alla Marvel, problemi di streaming di Disney+ e soluzioni Marvel.

Molti altri trailer Marvel presto: trailer di Avengers 5 Doomsday, trailer di Thunderbolts, trailer di Avengers 6 Secret Wars e trailer di Spider-Man Brand New Day!

üé§ Lyrics: Meghan Trainor - Like I'm Gonna Lose You ft. John Legend

I found myself dreamin' in silver and gold
Like a scene from a movie that every broken heart knows
We were walkin' on moonlight and you pulled me close
Split second and you disappeared and then I was all alone

[Pre-Chorus: Meghan Trainor]
I woke up in tears, with you by my side
A breath of relief, and I've realised
No, we're not promised tomorrow

I'm gonna hold you (Hey), like I'm saying goodbye
Wherever we're standin' (Yeah), I won't take you for granted
'Cause we'll never know when, when we'll run out of time
So I'm gonna love you (I'm gonna love you), like I'm gonna lose you (Like I'm gonna lose you)
I'm gonna love you (Love you), like I'm gonna lose you (Hey)

[Instrumental Bridge]

[Chorus: Meghan Trainor, John Legend, Both]
I'm gonna love you (Oh) like I'm gonna lose you (Like I'm gonna lose you)
I'm gonna hold you like I'm saying goodbye
Wherever we're standin', I won't take you for granted
'Cause we'll never know when, when we'll run out of time
So I'm gonna love you (I'm gonna love you, baby) like I'm gonna lose you (Like I'm gonna lose you)
I'm gonna love you (Oh) like I'm gonna lose you

snippet.title: Baylen Out Loud | Season 2 Official Trailer (TLC 2025)
snippet.description: Baylen Dupree is back for an all-new season of 'Baylen Out Loud,' premiering on Tuesday, Oct. 7 at 9 p.m. ET/PT on TLC. Season 2 sees Baylen, who lives with Tourette Syndrome, adjust to a more adult home life, now that she's living with fianc√© Colin. From pre-marital counseling sessions to cozy apartment life, this season is all about Baylen leveling up. As she adjusts to a new city, she begins building new friendships and expanding her support system. Baylen‚Äôs journey with Tourette Syndrome continues as she navigates new challenges, medications and opportunities to learn more about herself. With a wedding on the horizon, Baylen and Colin begin laying the groundwork for their big day, preparing what‚Äôs to come through dress shopping, floral design and venue visits, as they take meaningful steps toward building a life together. But wedding planning isn‚Äôt as dreamy as they imagined as they are faced with personal compromise, budget realities and location dilemmas that challenge their vision and test their teamwork.

snippet.title: Spider-Man: Alone | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Support the Series! Join Our Mission on Indiegogo: https://igg.me/at/spidermanalone

‚Äã‚ÄãOn this day in 1965, a new chapter was written. Today, a new story begins. This is the Official Indiegogo Trailer for Spider-Man: Alone.

‚ÄãThis is more than a fan film; it‚Äôs a deeply personal, character-driven series about the cost of becoming a hero. Inspired by a real-life battle with childhood cancer and a lifelong love for the character, our story plunges into the raw, often isolating, earliest days of a street-level Spider-Man. It's a modern reimagining of Amazing Fantasy #15 that asks: What does it take to be a hero?

‚ÄãEvery dollar pledged on our Indiegogo campaign is a vote of confidence, allowing our incredible team of artists to bring this cinematic vision to life. Your support helps us tell a story that believes that even in our most isolating moments, we can find the courage to just keep swinging.

‚ÄãThis project is also proud to launch our Inspired Action initiative in partnership with the non-profit Friendly Neighborhood Activist, aiming to turn on-screen heroism into real-world change.

‚ÄãFollow the Journey & Join Our Community:

Sostieni la serie! Unisciti alla nostra missione su Indiegogo: https://igg.me/at/spidermanalone

In questo giorno del 1965, un nuovo capitolo √® stato scritto. Oggi inizia una nuova storia. Questo √® il trailer ufficiale di Indiegogo per Spider-Man: Alone.

Questo √® pi√π di un fan film; √® una serie profondamente personale, incentrata sui personaggi, sul costo di diventare un eroe. Ispirata da una vera battaglia contro il cancro infantile e da un amore duraturo per il personaggio, la nostra storia si immerge nei primi giorni, crudi e spesso isolati, di uno Spider-Man di strada. √à una rivisitazione moderna di Amazing Fantasy #15 che si chiede: cosa ci vuole per essere un eroe?

Ogni dollaro donato alla nostra campagna Indiegogo √® un voto di fiducia, che permette al nostro incredibile team di artisti di dare vita a questa visione cinematografica. Il tuo supporto ci aiuta a raccontare una storia che ci fa credere che, anche nei momenti pi√π difficili, possiamo trovare il coraggio di continuare a combattere.

Questo progetto √® inoltre orgoglioso di lanciare la nostra iniziativa Inspired Action in collaborazione con l'organizzazione no-profit Friendly Neighborhood Activist, con l'obiettivo di trasformare l'eroismo sullo schermo in un cambiamento reale.

nl-NL.title: Spider-Man: Alone | Offici√´le trailer
nl-NL.description:
Steun de serie! Doe mee met onze missie op Indiegogo: https://igg.me/at/spidermanalone

‚Äã‚ÄãOp deze dag in 1965 werd een nieuw hoofdstuk geschreven. Vandaag begint een nieuw verhaal. Dit is de offici√´le Indiegogo-trailer voor Spider-Man: Alone.

‚ÄãDit is meer dan een fanfilm; het is een zeer persoonlijke, personagegedreven serie over de prijs die je betaalt om een ‚Äã‚Äãheld te worden. Ge√Ønspireerd door een echte strijd tegen kinderkanker en een levenslange liefde voor het personage, duikt ons verhaal in de rauwe, vaak isolerende, begindagen van een straatlegale Spider-Man. Het is een moderne herinterpretatie van Amazing Fantasy #15 die de vraag stelt: Wat is er nodig om een ‚Äã‚Äãheld te zijn?

‚ÄãElke dollar die wordt toegezegd voor onze Indiegogo-campagne is een blijk van vertrouwen, waardoor ons fantastische team van artiesten deze filmische visie tot leven kan brengen. Jouw steun helpt ons een verhaal te vertellen dat gelooft dat we zelfs in onze meest isolerende momenten de moed kunnen vinden om gewoon door te gaan.

Dit project is er ook trots op om ons Inspired Action-initiatief te lanceren, in samenwerking met de non-profitorganisatie Friendly Neighborhood Activist, met als doel heldendaden op het scherm om te zetten in echte verandering.

id.title: Spider-Man: Alone | Trailer Resmi
id.description:
Dukung Serial Ini! Bergabunglah dengan Misi Kami di Indiegogo: https://igg.me/at/spidermanalone

Pada hari ini di tahun 1965, babak baru telah ditulis. Hari ini, kisah baru dimulai. Ini adalah Trailer Resmi Indiegogo untuk Spider-Man: Alone.

Ini lebih dari sekadar film penggemar; ini adalah serial yang sangat personal dan berfokus pada karakter, tentang harga yang harus dibayar untuk menjadi seorang pahlawan. Terinspirasi oleh perjuangan nyata melawan kanker anak dan kecintaan seumur hidup terhadap karakter tersebut, kisah kami menyelami hari-hari awal Spider-Man jalanan yang masih mentah dan seringkali terisolasi. Ini adalah versi modern dari Amazing Fantasy #15 yang mempertanyakan: Apa yang dibutuhkan untuk menjadi seorang pahlawan?

Setiap dolar yang disumbangkan dalam kampanye Indiegogo kami merupakan sebuah tanda kepercayaan, yang memungkinkan tim seniman kami yang luar biasa untuk mewujudkan visi sinematik ini. Dukungan Anda membantu kami menceritakan kisah yang meyakini bahwa bahkan di saat-saat paling terisolasi sekalipun, kita dapat menemukan keberanian untuk terus berjuang.

Proyek ini juga dengan bangga meluncurkan inisiatif Aksi Terinspirasi kami, bekerja sama dengan organisasi nirlaba Friendly Neighborhood Activist, yang bertujuan untuk mengubah kepahlawanan di layar menjadi perubahan nyata di dunia.

Ikuti Perjalanan & Bergabunglah dengan Komunitas Kami:

snippet.title: God Of War (2025) - First Trailer | Dwayne Johnson
snippet.description:
#godofwar #godofwarmovie #dwaynejohnson 

Dwayne Johnson as Kratos. 

Editing, VFX, SFX, Thumbnail by @KHStudio please subscribe:
‚úÖ YouTube: https://bit.ly/KHstudio

üé• Attention viewers!

Please note that this video is a concept trailer created solely for artistic and entertainment purposes. I have meticulously incorporated various effects, sound design, AI technologies (Google Veo 3), movie analytics, and other elements to bring my vision to life. Its purpose is purely artistic, aiming to entertain and engage with the YouTube community. My goal is to showcase my creativity and storytelling skills through this trailer. Thank you for your support, and let's dive into the world of imagination! üçø

ü™ì  God of War Concept 

Whispers in Hollywood point toward a God of War adaptation, with Dwayne Johnson rumored to take on the role of Kratos. The idea of Johnson embodying the Spartan warrior has gained traction among fans who imagine his physicality translating into the brutal world of Greek mythology.

Reports suggest the story could follow the early years of Kratos, charting his rise from a Spartan general to the Ghost of Sparta. A focus on vengeance, loss, and redemption could provide the dramatic weight needed for a cinematic retelling.

The adaptation has been a longtime dream project for many studios, and Johnson‚Äôs involvement would add star power and global appeal to the potential franchise.

Feel free to express your thoughts on this exciting project by leaving a comment below.

snippet.title: ROBLOX NEED More Height
snippet.description:
ROBLOX NEED More Height Too short? get more height in this roblox game, also played a bonus karen game !

Like and Subscribe for more! 

Yes this is Lia and this is my new gaming channel Liabloxi where I will be uploading Roblox gaming videos

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It‚Äôs unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX ‚Äî interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything ‚Äî be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer ‚ÄúCapture the Flag‚Äù game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (‚ÄúRobux‚Äù). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

#roblox    #gaming

Talking about the absolute disaster that is the Ash & Iron "Major Update" Launch. The Destiny 2 Community is NOT HAPPY right now. An underwhelming Activity shoved into the portal, A Confusing Event, time-gated content, and Eververse Price increases. It's not going very well for Destiny 2.
--FOLLOW ME ON TWITCH: www.twitch.tv/kackishd

--- My Twitter: https://twitter.com/RickKackis

New #destiny2 video, going over the Ash & Iron Update Launch. We have new "Reclaim" Activity, New Territories Event, and the new Ash and Iron Rewards Pass (Ash and Iron Season Pass) in Season: Reclamation after the Destiny 2 News in the Latest TWAB (This week at Bungie) or TWID (This Week in Destiny) for September 4th, during Destiny 2: The Edge of Fate! The New Edge of Fate DLC Launch is Here! We have the New Year of Prophecy and Season: Renewal (Season of Renewal) that have gone live! We have a New Edge of Fate Campaign, and Kepler, the new Edge of Fate Destination! There are many Kepler Secrets to uncover! We also have the New Sieve Activity! And we have Armor 3.0, Destiny 2 Stats Overhaul, and the New Destiny 2 Portal! All leading to the New Destiny 2: Renegades Star Wars DLC!
The Ash and Iron Major Update is here! We return to the Plaguelands Location! We have new Legendary Weapons, and fan favorites like the MIDA Mini-Tool and Dreng! We also have New Exotic Weapons and a New Exotic Quest!
But today we're going over the new Ash and Iron Update, and the outrage within the Destiny 2 Community it has caused.
 #destiny2news #destiny2edgeoffate
